CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 4, 1961, pg. 25 reads:"Central Marks Youth Week - National Youth Week observance at Central Baptist Church included the "Call to Youth" program, on Tuesday evening, this week. Principals, left to right, were: Anita Pyles, Ronald Browne, Mrs. Gladys McNairy, adviser; John Eskridge, Atty. Livingston Johnson, speaker; Francine McNairy, Paul Jones and Clarence Rockamore. - Harris PHoto."
TitMainTitle: Anita Pyles, Ronald Browne, adviser Gladys McNairy, John Eskridge, speaker Atty. Livingston Johnson, Francine McNairy, Paul Jones, and Clarence Rockamore, gathered in Central Baptist Church for National Youth Week program
